@startuml createpostsequence

actor User
participant Browser
participant "Flask Controller" as Flask
participant "Posts DB (SQLite)" as PostsDB

User -> Browser : Fill out post form
Browser -> Flask : POST /posts
Flask -> Flask : Validate input
Flask -> PostsDB : INSERT post
PostsDB --> Flask : Success
Flask --> Browser : Redirect to homepage
Browser --> User : Updated post list
@enduml